This folder contains files used for unit testing and files that serve
as example scripts for GammaLib. For more test files and examples,
please check the instrument specific test folders inst/xxx/test.

test_XXX.cpp
  Unit test C++ files for GammaLib components.

test_python.py
  Unit test for GammaLib Python interface.

test_file_function.py
  Test the GModelSpectralFunc file function class.

example_model_xml_io.py
  Illustrates how gamma-ray source models are built and saved
  on disk into an XML file.

example_radial_models.py
  Illustrates how source models are accessed and used for
  create images. Tests also the correct normalization of the
  source models.
